<td tEditID="c1r1" style=" background-color:#FFFFFF; color:#000000; bEditID:r3st1; bLabel:main; font-size:12pt; font-family:arial;" aEditID="c1r1" locked="0" >
<![CDATA[<div style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: right;"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-family: 'Times New Roman', Times, serif; "><font class="Apple-style-span" color="#000066" size="6">{!Contact.SchoolText__c}</font></span></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: right;"><font class="Apple-style-span" face="'Times New Roman', Times, serif" color="#ff6600" size="4"><i>Chartered By The British Schools Foundation</i></font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: right;"><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial, sans-serif" color="#c0c0c0" size="6"><b><i><br></i></b></font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: right;"><font style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);" face="Arial, sans-serif"><br></font></div><div style="text-align: left;"><div style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial, sans-serif" size="4"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="border-spacing: 5px;">Dear&nbsp;{!Contact.Salutation} {!Contact.LastName},</span></font></div><div><span class="Apple-style-span" style="border-spacing: 5px;"><div style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font size="4"><br></font></div><div><div><div><div><div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="4"><font>The health and safety of your children is our top priority. In addition to taking all necessary&nbsp;</font><font>precautions, we aim to always keep our parents well informed of anything which comes to our&nbsp;</font>attention which may affect your children.&nbsp;</font></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="4"><br></font></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="4">I am writing to inform you that there has been a confirmed case of Impetigo in a pupil in one of our&nbsp;Year 2 classes. Impetigo is not usually a serious condition, it is infectious, and if not treated promptly&nbsp;complications may occasionally occur. It is a bacterial infection of the skin. It can cause small blisters&nbsp;on the skin which break and become covered with a yellow crust. Impetigo is usually spread by direct&nbsp;contact with someone who is infected or indirectly by sharing towels, face cloths, clothes or toys that&nbsp;have been used by someone who is infected. Your GP will usually prescribe an antibiotic ointment.&nbsp;Children should stay out of school until the sores have stopped blistering or crusting, or until 48 hours&nbsp;after starting appropriate treatment.</font></div><div><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: large;"><br></span></div><div><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: large;">For further information about impetigo please follow </span><a href="http://www.nhs.uk/conditions/impetigo/Pages/Introduction.aspx" style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: large;">this link.</a></div></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><br></div></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font size="4">Warm regards,</font></div></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">Alison Mackey&nbsp;</div><div style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><div><span style="font-family: arial;"><b>Deputy Head of Primary</b></span></div></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><br></div></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><br></div></div></span></div></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: left;"><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial, sans-serif">{!Contact.SchoolText__c}</font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: left;"><span class="Apple-style-span" style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><i><font class="Apple-style-span" color="#ff6600"><b>World Class Education</b></font></i></span></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: left;"><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial, sans-serif"><br></font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: left;"><font class="Apple-style-span" face="Arial, sans-serif">__________________________________________________________</font></div><div style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); text-align: center;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="1">{!User.School_List_Email_Footer__c}</font><font class="Apple-style-span" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;" face="Arial, sans-serif" size="1">&nbsp;</font></div>]]></td>
